{"tid":1472114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只想說一句：走到今天 多謝大家的努力","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T13:15:03.000Z","uid":280145,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ca0fdd0b9190efad305c3fe0cd9228f18a4fa0","tid":1472114,"uid":280145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">運動能走到今天 實屬不易 知道很多人都為昨晚的事件感到難過 甚至認為運動將逐漸消亡 <br />\n<br />\n事實上 14年後 很多人都感到無力 可是自6月開始 我從大家的身上得到許多力量 五大訴求異常清晰 各方用不同方法為我城努力 2個月以來民氣從未消減 比起5年前 我們都大大成長 <br />\n<br />\n社會運動 本是就是有高潮亦有低潮 但低谷又如何？我們香港人都不是第一次面對挫敗 也不是第一次面對政府、警察卑劣的手段 <br />\n<br />\n失敗與挫折教曉我們學會謙卑 教曉我們羅馬非一日建成 奪不走的是我們的良知和對公義的追求 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一起摸著石頭過河 我們都要勇敢的努力下去❤️<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"28532e7497f160b0c24b11f366f96eef26e2e14e","tid":1472114,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c